### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### Register
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "manager1",
  "email": "manager1@mail.com",
  "password": "Password1"
}

### Login
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "manager1",
  "password": "Password1"
}

### Set token manually from login response
@accessToken = REPLACE_ME
@refreshToken = REPLACE_ME

### Create product (ADMIN/MANAGER)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/productos
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "Laptop Enterprise",
  "descripcion": "ThinkPad para equipo backend",
  "precio": 1650.50
}

### List products with filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/productos?page=0&size=20&sort=createdAt,desc&search=laptop
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Soft delete (ADMIN)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/productos/1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Restore (ADMIN)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/productos/1/restore
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Refresh token
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

### Logout
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}
